---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="404 - Page Introuvable - INFODROP">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
        <div
            class="w-full max-w-lg rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 p-8 shadow-2xl flex flex-col items-center"
        >
            <div
                class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-yellow-500/10"
            >
                <svg
                    class="h-8 w-8 text-yellow-400"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <p
                class="text-7xl font-black bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >
                404
            </p>

            <h1
                class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl"
            >
                Page Introuvable
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-400">
                Le lien que vous avez suivi est peut-être cassé, ou la page a
                été supprimée. Vérifiez l'URL pour toute erreur de frappe.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-10">
                <a href="/" class="btn-primary"> ← Retour au Flux 24H </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
